    "body": "I have checked this and here is the current behavior.\r\n\r\nThe geth HTTP server returns status code `403 Forbidden` with body \"invalid host specified\" when the host does not match vhosts. For errors related to JWT, we return status `401 Unauthorized` with a response body stating the reason. \r\n\r\nSo the different cases can already be reasonably distinguished.",
